summary:
Project Manager with a focus on process design/transformation, continuous improvement, corporate controls design. Previous consulting experience in implementation and sustainment of control environments that utilize analytics, automation, and algorithms to manage risk, help strengthen business ops, and continuously monitor processes from both an effectiveness and efficiency perspective. 

Josh is a Chartered Professional Accountant (CPA) and is skilled in Financial Reporting, Internal Audit, SOX, Risk Assessment and Strategy, and Project Management. Currently pursuing a PMP certification.
